00:33:03.269 --> 00:33:07.304
it's getting time--let me just
finish saying something about

00:33:07.304 --> 00:33:10.450
this 10% to 25% getting rid of
the females,

00:33:10.450 --> 00:33:12.221
which again,
would reduce the population

00:33:12.221 --> 00:33:14.720
would lead you to not think
