that in Beijing along,

00:33:25.720 --> 00:33:28.880
Peking at the time,
several thousand babies,

00:33:28.880 --> 00:33:32.750
almost exclusively females,
were thrown into the streets

00:33:32.750 --> 00:33:37.114
