morning by carriers who dumped

00:33:37.114 --> 00:33:40.000
them into huge pits outside the
city.

00:33:40.000 --> 00:33:45.230
It sounds very much like Europe
of the similar time.

00:33:45.230 --> 00:33:48.509
What's interesting is that,
right now,

00:33:48.509 --> 00:33:51.538
China is approaching pretty
much the same female,

00:33:51.538 --> 00:33:54.400
with the sex selective
infanticide,

00:33:54.400 --> 00:33:58.806
pretty the same female deficit
that's been as far as we can

00:33:58.806 --> 00:34:02.902
tell a traditional level of it,
but now there's all this

00:34:02.902 --> 00:34:06.807
