these unmarried males and how it

00:34:06.807 --> 00:34:10.588
will utterly disrupt Chinese
society and it's a horrible sort

00:34:10.588 --> 00:34:11.469
of thing.
 

00:34:11.469 --> 00:34:13.260
Also, I think I mentioned this
before,

00:34:13.260 --> 00:34:17.510
as you've seen in Europe rather
than 10% to 25% of the males not

00:34:17.510 --> 00:34:20.882
