because of the deficit of

00:34:20.882 --> 00:34:23.490
females,
40%, 50%, and 60% of the males

00:34:23.490 --> 00:34:25.280
did not get married in Europe.
 

00:34:25.280 --> 00:34:31.369
I showed you the graphs of that
when we discussed Europe.

00:34:31.369 --> 00:34:35.280
The Chinese system,
fertility system,

00:34:35.280 --> 00:34:38.989
which keeps their population
manageable,

00:34:38.989 --> 00:34:44.760
not small but manageable,
is moderately early,

00:34:44.760 --> 00:34:47.394
not extremely early,
moderately early and nearly

00:34:47.394 --> 00:34:49.750
universal marriage of surviving
females.

00:34:49.750 --> 00:34:53.835
In 1998, for instance,
only 1% of Chinese women were

00:34:53.835 --> 00:34:57.904
unmarried by age 30,
whereas, in the west in that

00:34:57.904 --> 00:35:01.320
year 15% were unmarried 15 times
as much,

00:35:01.320 --> 00:35:05.650
