of Chinese and Chinese all the

00:35:20.228 --> 00:35:25.043
women got married,
but within marriage they had a

00:35:25.043 --> 00:35:27.070
low rate of fertility.
 

00:35:27.070 --> 00:35:31.077
You have to--you cut your
fertility down by half either by

00:35:31.077 --> 00:35:35.154
the European thing of less than
complete marriage or by the

00:35:35.154 --> 00:35:38.670
Chinese thing of less than
complete fertility.

00:35:38.670 --> 00:35:44.425
It looks like that fertility,
the total fertility rates

00:35:44.425 --> 00:35:50.820
should be more or less the same
between China and Europe,

00:35:50.820 --> 00:35:55.250
but by essentially opposite
kinds of fertility systems.

